        "color": 5,
        "width": 880,
        "height": 1120,
        "content": "## 📊 Google Sheets Setup\n\n1. Make a copy of the template spreadsheet:\n   👉 https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1OIo7K64HGvfUFufGYvAqxElVc0Ot65x3g-D5_w7ulLs/copy\n\n2. Copy the Spreadsheet ID from your copied sheet's URL:\n   `https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/【THIS IS THE ID】/edit`\n\n3. Replace the Spreadsheet ID in the following nodes with your copied sheet's ID:\n   - Read Monitor Targets\n   - Log to Check Log (OK)\n   - Log to Check Log (ERROR)\n   - Update alert_sent to TRUE\n\n4. Add your monitoring targets to the Monitor Targets sheet:\n   | name       | url                             | active |\n   |------------|-------------------------------|--------|\n   | Service A  | https://your-service.com/health | TRUE   |\n   | Service B  | https://api.example.com/ping    | TRUE   |\n\n   Set active to FALSE to temporarily disable a target without deleting the row.\n\n---\n\n## 📊 Google Sheetsセットアップ\n\n1. テンプレートスプレッドシートのコピーを作成：\n   👉 https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1OIo7K64HGvfUFufGYvAqxElVc0Ot65x3g-D5_w7ulLs/copy\n\n2. コピーしたスプレッドシートのURLからIDを取得：\n   `https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/【ここがID】/edit`\n\n3. 以下のノードのスプレッドシートIDをコピー先のIDに変更する：\n   - Read Monitor Targets\n   - Log to Check Log (OK)\n   - Log to Check Log (ERROR)\n   - Update alert_sent to TRUE\n\n4. Monitor TargetsシートにURLを追加する：\n   | name       | url                             | active |\n   |------------|---------------------------------|--------|\n   | Service A  | https://your-service.com/health | TRUE   |\n   | Service B  | https://api.example.com/ping    | TRUE   |\n\n   activeをFALSEにすることで、行を削除せずに一時的に監視を停止できます。"
